</b><br><br><br>And finally the woman who caused the whole damn mess, Blaine.<br><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1380431707ra/866489.gif" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br><br>Overall, this was an awesomely dark, messed up book. <b>READ IT PEOPLE!</b><br><br><i>A big thank you to my awesome friend Chrystal who let me borrow this book!</i></span>
